[
    {
        "content": "<p>Is there any sense in which the (op)indexed category</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mo>−</mo><mo>:</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>→</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">C</mi><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">t</mi></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">B/- : B \\to \\bf Cat</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">:</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">Cat</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>is universal?<br>\nIt sends every object to the slice over it and every morphism acts by postcomposition (not pb)</p>",
        "id": 298406707,
        "sender_full_name": "Matteo Capucci (he/him)",
        "timestamp": 1662997085
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I remember it was but I can't recall how.. It's not initial nor terminal, of course...</p>",
        "id": 298406871,
        "sender_full_name": "Matteo Capucci (he/him)",
        "timestamp": 1662997125
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Mmh I recalled this thread:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"#narrow/stream/229199-learning.3A-questions/topic/'Slice.20Yoneda\">https://categorytheory.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/229199-learning.3A-questions/topic/'Slice.20Yoneda</a>'</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>and I think what I was going at with my answer is what Streicher (Benabou?) calls 'fibred Yoneda lemma':<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/21317/ghNUxvGMavCFK5yHMER5MzMf/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/21317/ghNUxvGMavCFK5yHMER5MzMf/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/21317/ghNUxvGMavCFK5yHMER5MzMf/image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 298410772,
        "sender_full_name": "Matteo Capucci (he/him)",
        "timestamp": 1662998217
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Here <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Sp(P)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Sp</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> is defined as</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>I</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><munder accentunder=\"true\"><mi>I</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></munder><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Sp(P)(I) = Fib(B)(\\underline I, P)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Sp</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ib</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord underline\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.84em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"underline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>where in turn <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><munder accentunder=\"true\"><mi>I</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></munder><mo>=</mo><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>I</mi><mo><mover><mo><mo>→</mo></mo><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>d</mi></mrow></mover></mo><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\underline I = B/I \\overset{cod}\\to B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833em;vertical-align:-0.2em;\"></span><span class=\"mord underline\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.84em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"underline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.403em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\"><span class=\"mop op-limits\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.153em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span><span class=\"mop\">→</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.5669em;margin-left:0em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">co</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">d</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span></span></span></span></p>",
        "id": 298411110,
        "sender_full_name": "Matteo Capucci (he/him)",
        "timestamp": 1662998302
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Hence the statement reads</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>U</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>S</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>≅</mo><mi>S</mi><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>S</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><munder accentunder=\"true\"><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">−</mo><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></munder><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Fib(B)(U(S), P) \\cong Sp(B)(S, Fib(B)(\\underline -, P))</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ib</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0333em;vertical-align:-0.2833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Sp</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ib</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord underline\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.5833em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.7567em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"underline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">−</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2833em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mclose\">))</span></span></span></span></span></p>",
        "id": 298411332,
        "sender_full_name": "Matteo Capucci (he/him)",
        "timestamp": 1662998368
